{
  "stem": "17001.2",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 180.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So this way, you will have what to drink and will quenches your thirst.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my mother said, thank you very much.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I really appreciate that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So after he left, my mother said, who knows how many days we're going to be walking or traveling if he said that.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So sure enough, next day they made the announcement that everybody should pack and go to the lineup.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were counting you off and all of that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were in the ghetto about-- almost six weeks, almost six weeks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Meantime, just the night before we were taken away, this young man who looked like a Gypsy-- because, you know, some of the Jews, they were dark-skinned, dark, curly hair-- he came to my father and he said, Czigler [NON-ENGLISH], I'm going to disappear.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You never knew me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You never seen me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You don't know where I am, if I died, or if I went with my other-- with the other transfer.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm not available, but I want you to know about it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my mother-- my father said, OK.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he dressed up as a Gypsy and he even blackened his face more.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And during the night, the night before we were taken away, he just disappeared.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I never seen him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I have to break for a tape change.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
